B.Qp=new A.a4("If the fuel quantity drops below minimum, the aircraft must return to base.","Yak\u0131t miktar\u0131 minimumun alt\u0131na d\xfc\u015ferse u\xe7ak \xfcsse d\xf6nmelidir.","If the fuel quantity drops")
B.Sj=new A.a4("If the hydraulic system were to fail, the pilot would use backup controls.","Hidrolik sistem ar\u0131za yapsa pilot yedek kontrolleri kullan\u0131rd\u0131.","were to fail")
B.Qj=new A.a4("If maintenance had been performed on time, the fault would not have occurred.","Bak\u0131m zaman\u0131nda yap\u0131lsayd\u0131 ar\u0131za meydana gelmezdi.","had been performed")
