B.Qv=new A.a4("Subject to operational requirements, the interval may be extended by not more than 10 flight hours.","Operasyonel gerekliliklere ba\u011fl\u0131 olarak, interval en fazla 10 u\xe7u\u015f saati uzat\u0131labilir.","Subject to")
