B.Qi=new A.a4('"The crew failed to complete the checklist due to high workload during the approach phase."',"M\xfcrettebat, yakla\u015fma faz\u0131ndaki y\xfcksek i\u015f y\xfck\xfc nedeniyle kontrol listesini tamamlayamad\u0131.","failed to complete the checklist \u2026 high workload")
B.RE=new A.a4('"Assertiveness training helps crew members speak up when they identify a threat."',"Kendini ifade etme e\u011fitimi, ekip \xfcyelerinin bir tehdit fark ettiklerinde seslerini y\xfckseltmelerine yard\u0131mc\u0131 olur.","Assertiveness \u2026 speak up \u2026 identify a threat")
